    <title>鼠族本体及其拓展模组（持续更新）</title>
    <url>/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><p>本文章收录了鼠族模组本体和部分其拓展模组。本章不保证介绍全部拓展模组，模组介绍的排序也无顺序规律可言，玩家需自行检查DLC需求，前置模组，模组排序与兼容性问题。</p>
<h1 id="基础模组"><a href="#基础模组" class="headerlink" title="基础模组"></a>基础模组</h1><h2 id="New-Ratkin-Plus"><a href="#New-Ratkin-Plus" class="headerlink" title="New Ratkin Plus"></a>New Ratkin Plus</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/NewRatkinPlus.jpg" class="">  
<p>向游戏中加入了新的类人种族“萌鼠族(Ratkin)”。这种聪明机灵的吱星人有十分可爱的造型和萌萌的耳朵。以独特的中世纪造型风格为主。增加了一个叙述者——小鼠“罗蒂”,拥有众多的拓展mod。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1578693166&searchtext=New+Ratkin+Plus">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1578693166&amp;searchtext=New+Ratkin+Plus</a></p>
<h2 id="New-Ratkin-Plus简繁中文汉化"><a href="#New-Ratkin-Plus简繁中文汉化" class="headerlink" title="New Ratkin Plus简繁中文汉化"></a>New Ratkin Plus简繁中文汉化</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/NewRatkinPlus%E7%AE%80%E7%B9%81%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96.jpg" class="">  
<p>NewRatkinPlus的简繁汉化mod<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2898638732&searchtext=New+Ratkin+Plus">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2898638732&amp;searchtext=New+Ratkin+Plus</a></p>
<h1 id="装备拓展"><a href="#装备拓展" class="headerlink" title="装备拓展"></a>装备拓展</h1><h2 id="Ratkin-Appear"><a href="#Ratkin-Appear" class="headerlink" title="Ratkin Appear+"></a>Ratkin Appear+</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/RatkinApparel+.jpg" class="">  
<p>鼠族的服装拓展mod，新增了多种鼠族服装和装备，例如皮革护甲、东方风格连衣裙等。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2634067380&searchtext=Ratkin+Appear+">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2634067380&amp;searchtext=Ratkin+Appear%2B</a></p>
<h2 id="鼠族武器拓展-Ratkin-Weapons"><a href="#鼠族武器拓展-Ratkin-Weapons" class="headerlink" title="鼠族武器拓展 Ratkin Weapons+"></a>鼠族武器拓展 Ratkin Weapons+</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/Ratkinweapons+.jpg" class="">  
<p>添加了多种鼠族远程武器与近战武器，包括中世纪时代的与太空时代。也包括一些与战斗有关的其它内容，比如鼠族糖果制造与一些简单的鼠族服装。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2779404660&searchtext=Ratkin+Appear+">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2779404660&amp;searchtext=Ratkin+Appear%2B</a></p>
<h2 id="鼠族载具拓展-Ratkin-Vehicles"><a href="#鼠族载具拓展-Ratkin-Vehicles" class="headerlink" title="鼠族载具拓展 Ratkin Vehicles+"></a>鼠族载具拓展 Ratkin Vehicles+</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/RatkinVehicles+.jpg" class="">  
<p>为鼠族添加了部分地面、空中载具与对应的驾驶员套装，如鼠族飞艇、鼠族超重型坦克等、依赖于飞行器框架Aerocraft Framework与原版载具框架Vehicles Framework<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2959924062&searchtext=Ratkin+Appear+">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2959924062&amp;searchtext=Ratkin+Appear%2B</a></p>
<h2 id="鼠族远程武器拓展（新）"><a href="#鼠族远程武器拓展（新）" class="headerlink" title="鼠族远程武器拓展（新）"></a>鼠族远程武器拓展（新）</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/RatkinRangedWeaponExpandedNew.jpg" class="">  
<p>添加了数十种武器，从一战水平到太空时代皆有，以及一些固定的人操炮塔。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2928149958&searchtext=Ratkin">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2928149958&amp;searchtext=Ratkin</a></p>
<h2 id="鼠族机械体拓展"><a href="#鼠族机械体拓展" class="headerlink" title="鼠族机械体拓展"></a>鼠族机械体拓展</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/RatkinMechanoidExpanded.jpg" class="">  
<p>添加了具有鼠族特征的民用和军用机械体，可以胜任多种多样的工作和战斗需求。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2878476425&searchtext=Ratkin">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2878476425&amp;searchtext=Ratkin</a></p>
<h2 id="鼠族科技拓展-Ratkin-Technological-Expansion"><a href="#鼠族科技拓展-Ratkin-Technological-Expansion" class="headerlink" title="鼠族科技拓展 Ratkin Technological Expansion"></a>鼠族科技拓展 Ratkin Technological Expansion</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95.jpg" class="">  
<p>为鼠族添加了一些新的科技和工业时代的武器、炮台、药剂和设施等。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3298880009&searchtext=Ratkin">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3298880009&amp;searchtext=Ratkin</a></p>
<h1 id="背景-文化拓展"><a href="#背景-文化拓展" class="headerlink" title="背景&#x2F;文化拓展"></a>背景&#x2F;文化拓展</h1><h2 id="鼠族背景故事拓展"><a href="#鼠族背景故事拓展" class="headerlink" title="鼠族背景故事拓展"></a>鼠族背景故事拓展</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/RatkinBackStoryExpanded.jpg" class="">  
<p>为鼠族拓展了共206个的众多背景故事，包含141个成年背景故事和65个童年背景故事，以及两个新开局剧本。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3015200738&searchtext=Ratkin">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3015200738&amp;searchtext=Ratkin</a></p>
<h2 id="鼠族生活拓展-Ratkin-Lifestyle"><a href="#鼠族生活拓展-Ratkin-Lifestyle" class="headerlink" title="鼠族生活拓展 Ratkin Lifestyle+"></a>鼠族生活拓展 Ratkin Lifestyle+</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/Ratkinlifestyle+.jpg" class="">  
<p>添加了鼠族孩童衣物与一些复古风格的装饰，如风车、船、蜡烛等，为鼠族孩子添加了几件衣服，并替换了Biotech DLC中的课桌贴图，依赖于复古家具GloomyFurniture。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3263391066&searchtext=Ratkin">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3263391066&amp;searchtext=Ratkin</a></p>
<h1 id="派系拓展"><a href="#派系拓展" class="headerlink" title="派系拓展"></a>派系拓展</h1><h2 id="鼠族派系拓展-Ratkin-Faction"><a href="#鼠族派系拓展-Ratkin-Faction" class="headerlink" title="鼠族派系拓展 Ratkin Faction+"></a>鼠族派系拓展 Ratkin Faction+</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/RatkinFaction+.jpg" class="">  
<p>添加了一个默认敌对的鼠族派系-鼠族军阀。如果你不想和鼠族王国敌对或伤害可爱的鼠鼠，或者想寻求更多代入感，这个mod可能是适合你的。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3036302713&searchtext=Ratkin+Appear+">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3036302713&amp;searchtext=Ratkin+Appear%2B</a></p>
<h2 id="鼠族派系扩展：金鸢尾兰"><a href="#鼠族派系扩展：金鸢尾兰" class="headerlink" title="鼠族派系扩展：金鸢尾兰"></a>鼠族派系扩展：金鸢尾兰</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/%E9%87%91%E9%B8%A2%E5%B0%BE%E5%85%B0.jpg" class="">  
<p>内容众多的鼠族拓展，添加了一个来自银河系外的鼠族帝国：金鸢尾兰帝国，拥有特殊的袭击方式，派系交互与声望系统。包含众多新作物、枪械、近战武器、配件与头饰、服装与外套、建筑、鼠族科技、文化模因与4条新的戒律、3个新的基因，232个金鸢尾兰专属背景故事以及2位金鸢尾兰故事叙述者，7个新的事件与相关任务。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3159926804&searchtext=Ratkin">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3159926804&amp;searchtext=Ratkin</a></p>
<h2 id="鼠族扩展：桃花源-无治鼠邦"><a href="#鼠族扩展：桃花源-无治鼠邦" class="headerlink" title="鼠族扩展：桃花源-无治鼠邦"></a>鼠族扩展：桃花源-无治鼠邦</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/%E6%A1%83%E8%8A%B1%E6%BA%90%E9%BC%A0%E9%82%A6.jpg" class="">  
<p>增加了拥有东亚文化风格的鼠族独立阵营，其分为可供玩家正常交往，交易的鼠邦阵营；以及开局时敌对，但是可以通过外交手段改善关系的花札匪徒阵营。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3204817310&searchtext=Ratkin">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3204817310&amp;searchtext=Ratkin</a></p>
<h2 id="鼠族骑士团"><a href="#鼠族骑士团" class="headerlink" title="鼠族骑士团"></a>鼠族骑士团</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E9%AA%91%E5%A3%AB%E5%9B%A2.jpg" class="">  
<p>为鼠族添加了骑士团机制,可招募七种不同特点的骑士团友军，并可将殖民者送入骑士团进行训练。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3394862242&searchtext=Ratkin">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3394862242&amp;searchtext=Ratkin</a></p>
<h1 id="功能拓展"><a href="#功能拓展" class="headerlink" title="功能拓展"></a>功能拓展</h1><h2 id="鼠族CE补丁合集"><a href="#鼠族CE补丁合集" class="headerlink" title="鼠族CE补丁合集"></a>鼠族CE补丁合集</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/RatkinCEPatchCollection.jpg" class="">  
<p>鼠族本体及其众多拓展mod的CE补丁合集，并提供了新的子弹体系。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3301484845&searchtext=ratkin+CE">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3301484845&amp;searchtext=ratkin+CE</a></p>
<h2 id="鼠族异象拓展-Ratkin-Anomaly"><a href="#鼠族异象拓展-Ratkin-Anomaly" class="headerlink" title="鼠族异象拓展 Ratkin Anomaly+"></a>鼠族异象拓展 Ratkin Anomaly+</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/RatkinAnomaly+.jpg" class="">  
<p>添加了12种不同的黑暗异象与它们对应的仪式、科技等内容，分为六种初级异常与六种高级异常，大部分异象都有其对应的科技，包括装备、武器与实用物品，并且有其对应的的童话故事，需要异象Anomaly DLC。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3293914637&searchtext=Ratkin">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3293914637&amp;searchtext=Ratkin</a></p>
<h2 id="笨蛋的鼠族灵能拓展"><a href="#笨蛋的鼠族灵能拓展" class="headerlink" title="笨蛋的鼠族灵能拓展"></a>笨蛋的鼠族灵能拓展</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/%E7%AC%A8%E8%9B%8B%E7%9A%84%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E7%81%B5%E8%83%BD%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95.jpg" class="">  
<p>为鼠族添加了各种灵能能力，增添了18中不同功能的灵能职业。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3318518996&searchtext=%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E7%81%B5%E8%83%BD">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3318518996&amp;searchtext=%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E7%81%B5%E8%83%BD</a></p>
<h2 id="吱星人-鼠族基因扩展"><a href="#吱星人-鼠族基因扩展" class="headerlink" title="吱星人-鼠族基因扩展"></a>吱星人-鼠族基因扩展</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/%E5%90%B1%E6%98%9F%E4%BA%BA%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0.jpg" class="">  
<p>为鼠族增加了几种拥有不同特性的异种人，思路类似美狐，用意在于改变鼠族mod的基因异种有人类亚种的情况。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3043354134&searchtext=Ratkin">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3043354134&amp;searchtext=Ratkin</a></p>
<h2 id="金鸢尾兰鼠族基因扩展"><a href="#金鸢尾兰鼠族基因扩展" class="headerlink" title="金鸢尾兰鼠族基因扩展"></a>金鸢尾兰鼠族基因扩展</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/OA%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0.jpg" class="">  
<p>修改了塑形仓的塑形耗时与近视的具体效果，并添加了全新基因，以及文化模因。为鼠族添加了全新的外观基因、鼠族异种、独有的基因建筑、任务与事件、开局。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3300291918&searchtext=Ratkin">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3300291918&amp;searchtext=Ratkin</a></p>
<h2 id="鼠族辅助框架Ratkin-Auxiliary-framework"><a href="#鼠族辅助框架Ratkin-Auxiliary-framework" class="headerlink" title="鼠族辅助框架Ratkin Auxiliary framework"></a>鼠族辅助框架Ratkin Auxiliary framework</h2>  
<p>辅助框架，鼠族远程武器拓展和鼠族机械族均需要本模组。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2928149707&searchtext=Ratkin">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2928149707&amp;searchtext=Ratkin</a></p>
<h2 id="鼠族剧本扩展：风雪的遗孤"><a href="#鼠族剧本扩展：风雪的遗孤" class="headerlink" title="鼠族剧本扩展：风雪的遗孤"></a>鼠族剧本扩展：风雪的遗孤</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/%E9%A3%8E%E9%9B%AA%E9%81%97%E5%AD%A4.jpg" class="">  
<p>添加了数十个暴风雪衍生事件、数个新的世界事件、数个新的天气效果与事件、全新的暴风雪特效与遮罩层、专属的暴风雪相关建筑、新的的鼠族武器与服装，并且将在通关后解锁制作、新增植物、新种类的袭击，以及暴风雪中更加难缠的敌人、新增的结局任务“长路归乡”。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3381392312&searchtext=Ratkin">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3381392312&amp;searchtext=Ratkin</a></p>
<h1 id="美化模组"><a href="#美化模组" class="headerlink" title="美化模组"></a>美化模组</h1><h2 id="风信子的鼠族动态表情-Hyacinth’s-Ratkin-Facial-Animation"><a href="#风信子的鼠族动态表情-Hyacinth’s-Ratkin-Facial-Animation" class="headerlink" title="风信子的鼠族动态表情 Hyacinth’s Ratkin Facial Animation"></a>风信子的鼠族动态表情 Hyacinth’s Ratkin Facial Animation</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/RatkinFacialAnimation.jpg" class="">  
<p>为鼠族添加了其独特的动态表情，依赖于动态表情系列mod Facial Animation。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2852881266&searchtext=ratkin">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2852881266&amp;searchtext=ratkin</a></p>
<h2 id="Ratkin-Texture-Reset"><a href="#Ratkin-Texture-Reset" class="headerlink" title="Ratkin Texture Reset"></a>Ratkin Texture Reset</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/RatkinTexturesReset.jpg" class="">  
<p>将鼠族相关的贴图全部提升到1024x1024分辨率。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2870819859&searchtext=Ratkin+Texture+Reset">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2870819859&amp;searchtext=Ratkin+Texture+Reset</a></p>
<h2 id="鼠族贴图提升"><a href="#鼠族贴图提升" class="headerlink" title="鼠族贴图提升"></a>鼠族贴图提升</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E8%B4%B4%E5%9B%BE%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87.jpg" class="">  
<p>将鼠族相关的贴图全部提升到512x512分辨率，加载内存占用相比Ratkin Texture Reset更低，也更加清晰。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3383002343&searchtext=Ratkin+Texture+Reset">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3383002343&amp;searchtext=Ratkin+Texture+Reset</a></p>
<h2 id="鼠族身体贴图重制"><a href="#鼠族身体贴图重制" class="headerlink" title="鼠族身体贴图重制"></a>鼠族身体贴图重制</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93%E8%B4%B4%E5%9B%BE%E9%87%8D%E7%BD%AE.jpg" class="">  
<p>对鼠族本体成年和婴幼儿时期的贴图进行重置，并对头部贴图进行高清化。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3260369342&searchtext=Ratkin+Texture+Reset">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3260369342&amp;searchtext=Ratkin+Texture+Reset</a></p>
<h2 id="鼠族发型扩展"><a href="#鼠族发型扩展" class="headerlink" title="鼠族发型扩展"></a>鼠族发型扩展</h2><img src="/rwratkincnclub.github.io/2025/01/20/%E9%BC%A0%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84/RatkinhairstylesExpanded.jpg" class="">  
<p>为鼠族添加了五种新发型。<br><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3329107474&searchtext=Ratkin">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3329107474&amp;searchtext=Ratkin</a></p>
